* Build Universal Empire With This Engine

** Scripting Engine (Python)
** Networking Support
** Sound (if supported)
** Color (if supported)
** Quests
** Character Interaction
** Object Manipulation
** Navigation
** Save/Load System
** Client/Server Model for MMOs
** Command Line / OR Graphical Emulator
** Advanced Drawing Libraries
** Plugins
** Ability to add plugins to already started game / remove them without corruption


Basic Units:::

MapUnit, AdventureObject, AdventureActor, Quest
